  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK387">
<l>iṉcolā līttaḷikka vallāṟkkut taṉcolāṟ</l>
<l>ṟāṉkaṇ ṭaṉaittiv vulaku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The world will praise and submit itself to the mind of the king who is able to give with affability, and to protect all who come to him.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
